      "recording_attendee_id": "eae446f6-af58-4ab4-9acf-71743613fc78",
      "order_number": 25,
      "text": "Um so we actually have a marketing team. Um the management company is Range water, so we have a department um with our company that um that handles the marketing but what exactly um were you were you you know thinking"
