      "start_time": 118.8,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7dd8a0dd-9fec-4375-bb70-078bbc603a1a",
      "order_number": 26,
      "text": "Yeah, so um like I said I'm from rentable, we're a traditional and that we've got um obviously our website um and the communication network which includes realtor walk score, you loop. Um and a couple others that we just post your um available units to um but we also partnered with Facebook marketplace, um so we're able to list your available units on marketplace too. Um and we pre qualify all of those with a chat that's built in that is exclusive to rentable partners. Um"
    },
    {
      "id": "39e2adc2-af43-49e5-8ccf-25ccd8e2fc6b",
      "recording_id": "e313a648-2244-4349-8a84-495b127e7bdd",
      "end_time": 156.54,
      "start_time": 155.82,
      "recording_attendee_id": "eae446f6-af58-4ab4-9acf-71743613fc78",
      "order_number": 27,
