      "recording_id": "e313a648-2244-4349-8a84-495b127e7bdd",
      "end_time": 176,
      "start_time": 155.95,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7dd8a0dd-9fec-4375-bb70-078bbc603a1a",
      "order_number": 28,
      "text": "So that's to Facebook marketplace gets their name, uh phone number, email right off the bat. And then what unit they're interested in and when they would look to move in um as far as the data is concerned. Um So that's awesome. Everything that you're getting is pre qualified. Um Are you guys utilizing a property management software at this point?"
    },
