      "recording_attendee_id": "eae446f6-af58-4ab4-9acf-71743613fc78",
      "order_number": 29,
      "text": "uh Yes so we use"
    },
    {
      "id": "39e2adc2-af43-49e5-8ccf-25ccd8e2fc6b",
      "recording_id": "e313a648-2244-4349-8a84-495b127e7bdd",
      "end_time": 228.02,
      "start_time": 179.53,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7dd8a0dd-9fec-4375-bb70-078bbc603a1a",
      "order_number": 30,
      "text": "Okay, awesome. Yeah, we integrate within, so uh, we'll pull the listings directly from there. We're consistently checking those. We build those, um, listings manually into facebook marketplace. Um, and then we'll pull those directly onto our website and our partner Syndication network too. Um, the other thing that goes into that is we've got sponsored ads too. Um, so if you're ever on looking for a pair of shoes there, shoes, they follow you um on facebook instagram all your socials. That's the same idea here. Um, if they click on your listing in the facebook marketplace, um, we'll follow them on their news feed on facebook and on instagram. Um, and again, that chap, but is also built into those sponsored ads as well."
